TSI2S - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-invmgr-oper:inventory/racks/rack/{name}/powershelf/slot/{lot_name}/tsi1s/tsi1/{si1_name}/tsi2s/

Retrieve operation of resource: tsi2s

name: string
in path

ID of name

lot_name: string
in path

ID of lot_name

si1_name: string
in path

ID of si1_name

200 OK
tsi2s_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-invmgr-oper:inventory/racks/rack/{name}/powershelf/slot/{lot_name}/tsi1s/tsi1/{si1_name}/tsi2s/tsi2/{si2_name}/

in path

ID of name

lot_name: string
in path

ID of lot_name

in path

in path

ID of si2_name

TSI3S - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-invmgr-oper:inventory/racks/rack/{name}/powershelf/slot/{lot_name}/tsi1s/tsi1/{si1_name}/tsi2s/tsi2/{si2_name}/tsi3s/

Retrieve operation of resource: tsi3s

name: string
in path

ID of name

lot_name: string
in path

ID of lot_name

si1_name: string
in path

ID of si1_name

si2_name: string
in path

ID of si2_name

200 OK
tsi3s_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

TSI4S - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-invmgr-oper:inventory/racks/rack/{name}/powershelf/slot/{lot_name}/tsi1s/tsi1/{si1_name}/tsi2s/tsi2/{si2_name}/tsi3s/tsi3/{si3_name}/tsi4s/

in path

in path

ID of si1_name

in path

ID of si2_name
